---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageCard from '../components/PageCard.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <PageCard title="FAQs" subtitle="Everything you need to know">
    <div class="faq-accordion">
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>What is the dress code?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>We kindly request formal attire. For men, this means a suit and tie. For women, an elegant cocktail dress or full-length gown is perfect.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>Are children invited?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>While we love your little ones, our wedding is an adults-only event so that everyone can relax and enjoy the evening.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>Is there a hotel block?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Yes, we have reserved a block of rooms at the nearby Grand Hotel. Please mention our names when booking to receive the discounted rate.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>Will the ceremony be indoors or outdoors?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Weather permitting, the ceremony will take place outdoors in the garden. The reception will be held indoors.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </PageCard>
</Layout>

<style>
  .faq-accordion {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-sage);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(42,46,41,0.03);
  }

  .faq-item[open] {
    border-color: var(--text-dark); /* Highlight border when open */
  }

  summary {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none; /* Hide default arrow */
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    user-select: none;
  }

  summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: '-';
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-content {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in-out;
  }

  .faq-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--accent-sage);
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    summary {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
